; Regression test for issue #623: Virtual transactions cause unbalanced equity report (BZ#623)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/623
;
; The equity command includes virtual postings (e.g., (Budget:Food)) in the
; "Opening Balances" transaction without adding a corresponding virtual equity
; entry to balance them. This makes the equity output unbalanced when reimported.

2024/01/01 Opening
    Assets:Checking    $1000.00
    Equity:Opening    $-1000.00

2024/01/15 Purchase
    Expenses:Food       $50.00
    Assets:Checking    $-50.00
    (Budget:Food)       $50.00

test equity
2024/01/15 Opening Balances
    Assets:Checking                          $950.00
    (Budget:Food)                             $50.00
    Equity:Opening                         $-1000.00
    Expenses:Food                             $50.00
end test
